All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<Key,​ObjectSet<Value>>
public class MultiSet<Key,​Value> extends BaseMap<Key,​ObjectSet<Value>>
A map from key to an ObjectSet of values. Values can be added with add(Object, Object). A flattened set of all values in the map can be retrieved with flatValues(). The ObjectSet for a key can be retrieved with set(Object). If the set for the given key does not yet exist, one is created.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
